    • Constructor Detail

      • JeopardyGame

        public JeopardyGame()
        Creates a new JeopardyGame with default characteristics.

      • JeopardyGame

        public JeopardyGame(Category[] chosenCategories,
                    Category[] allCategories,
                    int numberOfPlayers,
                    int numberOfRounds,
                    int numberOfAnswers,
                    int currentRoundNumber)
        Creates a new JeopardyGame with the specified game data.
        Parameters:
        chosenCategories - the categories chosen in the game launcher to use in this game of jeopardy
        allCategories - all the categories read from the data file
        numberOfPlayers - the number of players in this game of jeopardy; must be higher than JeopardyGame.MINIMUM_NUMBER_OF_PLAYERS and lower than JeopardyGame.MAXIMUM_NUMBER_OF_PLAYERS
        numberOfRounds - the number of rounds in this game of jeopardy; must be higher than JeopardyGame.MINIMUM_NUMBER_OF_ROUNDS and lower than JeopardyGame.MAXIMUM_NUMBER_OF_ROUNDS
        numberOfAnswers - the number of answers per category in this game of jeopardy; must be higher than JeopardyGame.MINIMUM_NUMBER_OF_ANSWERS and lower than JeopardyGame.MAXIMUM_NUMBER_OF_ANSWERS
        currentRoundNumber - the current round number
